node version key thing installed: 14.x

all nginx file are located in /etc/nginx/

folders containing site code are located in /var/www/html/

to build a react app run the following commands

1) git clone <url>
2) npm install
3) npm run build


test nginx syntax: sudo ngninx -t
restart nginx: sudo service nginx restart
to publish a site do the following 
1) build the static html page
2) move the build folder to /var/www/html/
3) rename the folder to the name of the website it should fall under
